com.contentful.java.cma

Class CMAClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.contentful.java.cma.CMAClient

  • public class CMAClient
extends java.lang.Object
    The CMAClient is used to request information from the server. Contrary to the delivery API, a client is not associated with one Space, but with one user.
